c: 18
v: 21
t: "In that miraculous manner, We made them (the people) stumble upon (that cave). So that they would know for sure that Allah´s promise is real, and that there is no doubt about the hour (of judgment). But instead, they carried on their dispute and said, \"Let us build a monument over them. Only their Lord knows the truth about them!\" Those who were in charge said, \"We shall definitely turn the site into a place of worship"